Dear Professor Toliver,<br><br>
One hour for Vietnam? Wow! But given that your class is titled Western Civilization, it is impressive that you are able to fit anything in at all. I would like to receive your outline and information on your Honors Class on Viet Nam. <br><br>
My mailing address is: Department of Nutrition, University of California, Davis, CA 95615. <br><br>
I am a nutritional geographer, not a historian or a political scientist; my publications on Viet Nam are few and in the area of nutrition. <br><br>
